<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c4">[القنوع]</span>: الكثير القناعة.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>... فَعِيل<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
